><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tdr1665702729081.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tdr1665702729081.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tdr1665702729081.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tdr1665702729081\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      wildcard literals\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Allow wildcard literals in actual data.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__topic_d50495e1_d50496e1_d50497e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__p_d50498e1_d50499e1_d50500e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">wildcard literals</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__section_j4j_fbl_3cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d769146e63\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__p_d50504e1_d50505e1_d50506e1\">This option is applicable only for wildcard literals\n            used in Uniface retrieve profiles. <code class=\"ph codeph\">wildcard literals</code> is not supported\n            in combination with <code class=\"ph codeph\">multi byte</code> .</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__section_mrn_gbl_3cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d769146e78\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__p_d50510e1_d50511e1_d50512e1\">If this option is set, when a wildcard literal is\n            included in the actual data, it is escaped out so Informix does not treat it as a\n            wildcard.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tdr1665702729081__p_d50513e1_d50514e1_d50515e1\">If this option is not present, no wildcard literals\n            are allowed.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vda1665702728733.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>multi byte</a><p>Enable multi-byte character sets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532301\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532301\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "wildcard literals Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 wildcard literals Allow wildcard literals in actual data. USYS$INF_PARAMS wildcard literals Use This option is applicable only for wildcard literals used in Uniface retrieve profiles. wildcard literals is not supported in combination with multi byte . Description If this option is set, when a wildcard literal is included in the actual data, it is escaped out so Informix does not treat it as a wildcard. If this option is not present, no wildcard literals are allowed. Related Links multi byte Enable multi-byte character sets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}